data.description: Like New Home in Juliana's Garden gated community at City in the Hills! Why wait for new construction when you can have this home with 3 bedrooms plus an office, 2.5 bathrooms and OWNED SOLAR. There is a large gourmet kitchen including an island with sink, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and kitchen nook. The nook has French doors which open to the backyard. There is wood flooring throughout most of the home, including the master bedroom. The family room is cozy with a fire place. The backyard has a covered patio, wood deck, and built in barbecue. The master suite has two walk in closets, a soaking tub, a large shower, and two walk in closets. The office has lots of light with French doors to the front courtyard and large windows looking out to the small park across the street.
